{"tid":1786792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AIA歐陸嘉年華澄清網上傳聞","createTime":"2019-12-17T11:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T07:34:18.000Z","uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":397,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4b399bd18c22f013641cec7bf7a8a2c32922e9","tid":1786792,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"【歐陸嘉年華主辦方澄清：】<br />\n<br />\n歐陸嘉年華從來沒有對訪客穿衣有任何特定限制或規定, 訪客有個人自由選擇衣服的顏色。嘉年華是一個適合一家大細的活動，嘉年華的機動遊戲及攤位遊戲已開放，歡迎大家𦲷臨與家人好友歡渡時光。<br />\n<br />\n有關嘉年華每年舉辦的媒體日，大會均邀請媒體好友免費體驗嘉年華，並贈送一個毛公仔以表我們感謝媒體支持的小心意。<br />\n<br />\n【Clarification from the Producers of The Great European Carnival】<br />\n<br />\nThe Great European Carnival has never had a dress code.  Our guests can wear what ever combination of colour whilst they enjoy their Carnival experience.  It is a family friendly event. Our gates are open to all generations. We look forward to welcoming you all very soon.  Our rides and games are ready.<br />\n<br />\nFor the avoidance of doubt The Great European Carnival invites media every year. All media are given the opportunity to experience the rides and games for free and are provided with a complimentary cuddly toy."},{"pid":"8c418429f1a83bebafd04471af4dd6a1eaaa5dab","tid":1786792,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7289336ccb03db42338955dd88960f921f06a3","tid":1786792,"uid":77937,"like":350,"dislike":13,"score":337,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:51:47.000Z","msg":"驚呀屌你老母？收皮啦唔撚想去"},{"pid":"fa241ecb0ad111c1a87055e138bda9c3392cd438","tid":1786792,"uid":53672,"like":214,"dislike":0,"score":214,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"咩fc就咁一張圖話有就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我話我係光頭sir都得啦"},{"pid":"0d94917ffe995526bd502614e3320b24d34283ad","tid":1786792,"uid":27